| Topic | Producer | Consumer | Status |
|---|---|---|---|
| `incident.created` | Firewall Service | Incident Service | ✅ Working (schema mismatch with REST API) |
| `incident.stored` | Incident Service | Firewall AI Worker | ✅ Working |
| `incident.analyzed` | Firewall AI Worker | Incident Service | ✅ Working |
| `audit.event` | Incident Service | Audit Service | ✅ Working |
| `alert.created` | Incident Service | Audit Service, Notification Service | ⚠️ Always fires (should be conditional) |
| `ingest.analyzed` | — | — | ❌ Not implemented |
| `policy.violation` | — | — | ❌ Not implemented |

